{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897250/extras/steam-store-title-about.png?t=1737867360\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A mining visual novel set deep beneath a snow-covered mine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you progress through the mines, you can upgrade your tools and uncover the story of why you came to this place. A gentle tale that offers small yet satisfying accomplishments on sleepless nights.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897250/extras/steam-header-main.gif?t=1737867360\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897250/extras/steam-store-title-highlights.png?t=1737867360\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Mining Game x Visual Novel</strong>: A unique experience where digging deeper advances the story.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Relaxation in a Short Session</strong>: A serene journey lasting about two hours, accompanied by calming music and storytelling.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Satisfying Mining Mechanics</strong>: Enjoy the rewarding sound effects of discovering ores and the joy of upgrading your equipment as you delve deeper.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897250/extras/steam_header1.png?t=1737867360\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897250/extras/steam-store-title-story.png?t=1737867360\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The beginning of a harsh and e